snippet: New England Patriots tight end Rob Gronkowski has a suspected punctured lung and is likely to miss Sunday's game against San Francisco, the NFL website reported on Monday....
lead_paragraph: New England Patriots tight end Rob Gronkowski has a suspected punctured lung and is likely to miss Sunday's game against San Francisco, the NFL website reported on Monday.

headline.main: Pats Tight End Gronkowski Likely to Miss 49ers Clash
headline.print_headline: Pats Tight End Gronkowski Likely to Miss 49ers Clash
